high_descs: Grab the apple on the table.
Carrying the apple, turn around and walk to the fridge to your right.
Place the apple in the fridge to chill it, then remove it.
Carrying the cold apple, turn around and walk to the microwave to your right.
Place the cold apple on the plate in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold apple on a plate in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk around to the other side of the counter in front of you.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Walk around the counter and ahead to the fridge.
Place the apple in the fridge to the left of the lettuce. Close the door, wait a moment, and take the apple out again.
Turn around and veer right to the microwave.
Place the apple in the microwave to the right of the glass.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple in a microwave.

high_descs: Walk left and forward to the left side of the rounded counter
Pick up the red apple from the counter
Turn right and walk over to the fridge
Put the apple into the fridge then remove it
Turn around and walk over to the microwave left of the dishwasher
Put the apple in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled red apple in the microwave
